Reasoning: The paper discusses software visualization, which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE). The focus of the paper is on the visualization of the evolution of models in Model-Driven Software Evolution, which falls under the category of software development (cs.SD). The paper also mentions the use of visualization tools/CASE tools, which are related to programming languages (cs.PL). The paper emphasizes the importance of visualization for better understanding complex phenomena, which is related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Finally, the paper proposes a framework for assessing the Model Driven Software Evolution process, which can be considered as a topic related to cybernetics (cs.CY).
